                        <salute>My dear Mr Neihardt</salute>
                    </opener>
                    <p>This speaks for itself = I trust you don't find my letter difficult &#8212; and feel like a <unclear/> who <unclear/> &#8212; I received your beautiful letter, what was it all about.</p>
                    
                    <p>I in this <unclear/> but it gives me the chance to thee again.</p>
                        
                    <p>The warmest wishes from the House of Adelman.</p>
